@startuml App State Machine
hide empty description
[*] --> Capture
Capture --> Preprocess
Preprocess --> Extracting
Extracting --> Confirm : Success
Extracting --> ExtractError : Failure
ExtractError --> Extracting : Retry
ExtractError --> Capture : Cancel
Confirm --> Sending : Accept
Confirm --> Extracting : Retry
Confirm --> Capture : Deny
Sending --> Capture : Success
Sending --> SendError : Failure
SendError --> Sending : Retry
SendError --> Confirm : Back
@enduml
